43dc8bb39c5892411512fbc","tid":315702,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"係唔係食屎食上腦<br />\n日本醫療出名差<br />\n真心想醫好個病就去美國啦<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地都唔係真心想好返架啦<br />\n純粹戀日戀上腦咁解"},{"pid":"c1ac6d1ab6e21d9c6780ba026479bf00daf7b1c2","tid":315702,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係食屎食上腦<br />\n日本醫療出名差<br />\n真心想醫好個病就去美國啦<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地都唔係真心想好返架啦<br />\n純粹戀日戀上腦咁解</blockquote><br />\n有幾出名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3c9d031f423eb1c4257113dff68480ee6ec47b","tid":315702,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係唔係食屎食上腦<br />\n日本醫療出名差<br />\n真心想醫好個病就去美國啦<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地都唔係真心想好返架啦<br />\n純粹戀日戀上腦咁解</blockquote><br />\n有幾出名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近日本咪好出名小林xx女主播死左既<br />\n正常你如果係外國真係第一流醫療係唔會咁遲先發現到<br />\n<br />\n日本人種太純係其中一個主要原因<br />\n病例太少，又唔肯多d同外國交流<br />\n好話唔好聽，台灣既醫療都勁過佢"},{"pid":"b68c2ccd92e945f97347d046258dc9f4c438460a","tid":315702,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年731部隊搵中國人做實驗，今日中國人重金請日本人開刀，贏家一直都係日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5698193ba857366c4cd76e8f60af371b908f19be","tid":315702,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"真心覺得中國人連死，都想醫死係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7352359b11e541240ec5d30666ca606b94c4e613","tid":315702,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"Doctor x"}]}